Vicky Longley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vicky_Longley 0 Victoria "Vicky" Jane Longley (born 26 October 1988 in Bromley, London) is an English actress and singer. She played Emma Norton in the children's comedy Genie in the House, screened in the UK and The Netherlands on Nickelodeon, and in France on Canal J, and studied performing arts at the Italia Conti Academy of Theatre Arts.
